{"tid":1510203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[代post][文長]唔啱聽嘅說話你想唔想聽？(反送中)","createTime":"2019-08-27T05:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:17:19.000Z","uid":271554,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"739d9b81649c08f4b9c5e09ac05b66052fbc494c","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"無account要借fd出post，負皮預咗，而且會逆好多人意見兼完全打破大家堅持嘅思維模式，今次一定要有心理準備作長期同多方位嘅抗戰，一定要兄弟爬山先可以成事，跪求大家睇晒佢再思考再進化<br />\n<br />\n腦裡面好多諗法，但無辦法一對手做到，睇下回應再決定出唔出第二篇&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第一</span>，作為一個前紀律部隊，輕輕講一句：前晚popo無射示威者好好彩<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>你幾十萬個不情願都好：前晚係有200%條件向示威者開槍</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>點解唔咁做，大家要諗諗</strong></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n個人推測係有人落咗死命令唔准開槍射人，一開槍就交人<br />\n<br />\n佢地捉咗義士起勢咁打，就係可能因為無得用致命武力，所以要喺其他地方發洩。今日員佐級協會嘅聲明已經落order（係落order呀，依家邊個紅色Ｄ先？）叫「警隊管理層重新檢視現時以驅散為主的行動策略及武力使用方案」，我覺得已經係一個提示<br />\n<br />\n而且，popo幾錯都好，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔使喺呢個stage清算，前線精力人手有限唔好將個焦點擺落去住</span>，呢條戰線有機會再講<br />\n<br />\n所以，勇武手足更加要審慎行事，作為冷氣軍師真係唔適合畀咩意見，只係唔想再見到有人被捕被虐，我認咁諗好自私，但大家要避免熱血上腦，但只有一句：「太慢喇！」（雖然仲有好多嘢想講）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第二</span>，因為要撐到10月1同11月區選，所以我講嘅會係和理非、非送頭路線，同埋會係面向內地同本土，美國同國際注意力果邊兄弟請繼續爬山唔好停<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n講到內地，大家一定反感，但唔好唔記得啊偉大發言人「愁眉耿爽」講過：「14億人都有話語權！」<br />\n<br />\n我有個熟悉國情嘅朋友（黃色）曾經講過，好欣賞反送中遊行拎中國國旗嘅人出嚟，係呀──中國國旗！<br />\n <br />\n700萬 vs 14億，盲嘅都知打次飛機都無14億啦<br />\n<br />\n今年中國嘅主題係「維穩」，而維穩費一早已經超出咗軍費，所以一定要令14億人知道自己「真係有話語權」，姑勿論佢地點仇視香港都好，令佢地覺醒創造不可能係其中一個可行嘅途徑，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼續煲大維穩費</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">依家國內就係挑起14億人對香港嘅仇視</span>──透過滲透挑起現場手足情緒，做假、移花接目、Fake news、改圖，甚至自編自導(喺機場自製黑衣人追打人嘅片段 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rk3tyHp3_lg&amp;list=LL27mjI_iZfrm3KoxNcIfN9Q&amp;index=3&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRk3tyHp3_lg%26list%3DLL27mjI_iZfrm3KoxNcIfN9Q%26index%3D3%26t%3D0s&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bixzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=b16b9a09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rk3tyHp3_lg&amp;list=LL27mjI_iZfrm3KoxNcIfN9Q&amp;index=3&amp;t=0s</a> ) 目的就係利用資訊接收被過濾被改寫而令14億人好團結咁仇視香港人<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌拎國旗呢關心理關口真係好撚難過！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">難過得過睇住義士畀人打但又做唔到嘢、而佢地又要面對漫長嘅官司、長時間嘅牢獄之苦同失去咗嘅前途？</span><br />\n如果自己連呢少少嘅面子同堅持都擺唔低，就此Skip咗呢篇嘢，負皮都唔使畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n呢個Stage係要講手段，而講手段得嚟就可能要擺低樽鹽，仲要唔犯法，好撚難的。問題係有無勇氣去做？<strong><ins>唔好畀咁多觀念束縛住</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n點令到自己舒服Ｄ？你睇下，721白衣人、荃灣斬人班黑社會、北角福建幫，拎住國旗打人斬人無包袱，popo見到又必畏懼兼必侚私，就知國旗係護身符啦，你估佢地真係咁愛國？國旗於佢地嚟講道具嚟架咋，所以真係唔使有心理包袱<br />\n<br />\n如果831可以遊行，如果遊行有一百萬人，如果一百萬人都拎住國旗同區旗，一片血染的風采會係點？首先，官媒一定講一百萬人上街支持中國，即係無藉口強力鎮壓。第二，官媒又敢唔敢真係報有一百萬人上街？三，中國嘅地方（唔鍾意都好，暫時都係）可以有一百萬人上街，只有香港有，國內有十萬人上街，會變成點嘅樣？即刻鎮壓GG啦<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n目標係好似Inception套戲咁，種一個想法入國內人腦入面。要佢地開始會諗，點解香港有得遊行，國內無？其者開始有其他有機會動搖國內維穩力量嘅想法<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">另外，試下標語改改佢：<br />\n<br />\n「14亿人的话语权呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「微博之外还有其他世界，挡着你前进前前进的只是一道墙」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「言論自由是权利，游行是权利，宗教自由是权利，同胞，您值得拥有」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「说好的新闻自由呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「人人都值得拥有投票权，中国人比西方人更值得」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「钱赚得够多了，但自由还是要挣的」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「你看什么啊你？我有私隐权！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n呢Ｄ標語官媒又敢唔敢刊登？如果有人真心咗，將呢Ｄ標語送到微博/透過微信傳返去&hellip;&hellip;<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雖然去到最尾一定會有扭曲的，好有可能話打著紅旗反紅旗，但依家去到今時今日，係咪可以一試呢？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n仲有要講愛國丫嘛，點會少得 Ｄ插晒旗嘅法拉利<br />\nshorturl.at/rxyJK<br />\n文宣組可以做嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主依家唔使講住，因為佢地被教育到民主唔一定好過現有體制。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n都係果句，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>一定要有心理準備作長期同多方位嘅抗戰<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n另外仲有幾條本地長期戰線可以一試，睇下各位反應如何&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"73cddd6c850a1bc1a4c858e04aa5e3811b563606","tid":1510203,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bixzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=41f8bb24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bixzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=28f8ee88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bixzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=dff8034d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"28ac417fd4728aefb70c2b07d1bb6813bc17bdfb","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a71eca82eb7b8bbd38eb24a2477c7490dc1ae38c","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d8dc93f322467571b5b245d8253f2c7a9fdef1e","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"忘記了p牌推唔推到文"},{"pid":"a195afb0bcffeb0309209c3b566ac840dcdc0577","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:56:45.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"cf8340829bfa8763ee2429e8f6e5c9900f5f2ac0","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe2f96dddee88eb5ab0bb564e31e808b21c8be58","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17faf6c3bafc6f23ff6e2d7ef7265dd03930c44b","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"063c11f7373d0a591adc463394c811a35db78027","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d4505d514978207e36ef02f8f74faaf4ee673da","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27f4473c6d4b7d96fa85436120b08c2239a4676c","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"601730afad1d83d5b3c235aa91060259daf93e1f","tid":1510203,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"043e5573555e446afec02ff607fcd320e4d2a603","tid":1510203,"uid":184488,"like